":"pish<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/De23GXK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDe23GXK.png&h=eb6b09eb&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mUks8CK.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmUks8CK.gif&h=c52291c1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CzNWhv4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCzNWhv4.gif&h=49c6f20d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yAA5aQ4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyAA5aQ4.gif&h=b03e4a86&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SDJ2Xv4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSDJ2Xv4.gif&h=989dacc3&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g8H7pa4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg8H7pa4.gif&h=03eefc52&s={SIZE}\" /> </div>"},{"pid":"cc54e0e15c85c0ebcf0c49a9340b19fcbb049021","tid":1317650,"uid":2764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T20:32:02.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7a0afd72988a4ffd3c13e47e43a520f30131f1b5","tid":1317650,"uid":151256,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T20:32:10.000Z","msg":"好文共賞<br />\n<br />\n但香港無得同當時嘅法國比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港人讀書多有飽飯食，有太多顧慮<br />\n<br />\n香港人欠義士同年輕人嘅實在太多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"add284a1a09a2823b1c9ef137de3e901aec6e30d","tid":1317650,"uid":2429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T20:32:54.000Z","msg":"係，北京已經直接接管咗警隊，我哋一輸所有人都會被清算。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dedb919c5e8014c0fa6ae68906ae2b1d97d0bf4","tid":1317650,"uid":150753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T20:42:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"13c9783ff1e415fd9b1d4dc4fadc4a1f912b0009","tid":1317650,"uid":59886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T23:13:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b0cda93b9321f1dd192b645f9d21e4345f77db1c","tid":1317650,"uid":622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T02:28:57.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8acbb6967897b9e0a739c1f988b50113d243612","tid":1317650,"uid":126283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T05:40:54.000Z","msg":"革命既發生可能係一瞬間既事<br />\n前線做緊野後方都未必知<br />\n所以大家一定要有爆發革命既心理準備<br />\n有心理準備總好過臨場驚慌<br />\n<br />\n尤其老弱幼要小心<br />\n啲狗終有一日會追住黎咬"},{"pid":"6a30df815f6744711c7539142b5b6cf395fdf694","tid":1317650,"uid":69472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T05:43:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"688ceaf55c02fa4507aa0add9899e7f008881f5a","tid":1317650,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T05:59:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/Ud1DpEH.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUd1DpEH.gif&h=84b3817f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"78ff2026c5068aaf07a19dd4bb5866c05f33da7e","tid":1317650,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"688ceaf55c02fa4507aa0add9899e7f008881f5a","tid":1317650,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T05:59:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/Ud1DpEH.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUd1DpEH.gif&h=84b3817f&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T06:04:18.000Z","msg":"唔好再post依張垃圾圖害死人啦，琴晚個阿伯都識捉實渣棍隻右爪。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a26a8502dcb6179bd8296e80ba2e4465684a4ff","tid":1317650,"uid":92347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T06:17:06.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"7bbb5e83464fa97318b902ee769d7108aa88681e","tid":1317650,"uid":126283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:55:22.000Z","msg":"呢場係賭身家既戰爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n怯就真係輸一世<br />\n黑暗係漫長<br />\n但只要堅持<br />\n光明一定會出現"},{"pid":"0b46e554f4aa5eb0dda4ebc532a56fddd18aed25","tid":1317650,"uid":237712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17:11:41.000Z","msg":"P"},{"pid":"c2f22004524d0b5051e0a88393b5fabf731f2600","tid":1317650,"uid":126283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17:20:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"386333aa2b5eedde8839e0a11131c997ddf7b481","tid":1317650,"uid":126283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T01:36:38.000Z","msg":"林鄭諗緊分區解嚴呢啲屎忽野<br />\n一旦解嚴外資即走<br />\n香港就永遠冇得翻身<br />\n大家既日常生活都唔能夠回復正常<br />\n連買件衫食個包都成問題<br />\n失業、破產、殺人越貨一定會發生<br />\n淨係咁已經有革命既正當性"},{"pid":"43393636c9a70cfcf270a9025bd22e7d27f05c06","tid":1317650,"uid":126283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T08:12:16.000Z","msg":"記住，我地對抗緊既係極權政府<br />\n如果唔能夠令極權政府跪低<br />\n我哋就必定被秋後算帳<br />\n<br />\n而保證大家不被算帳<br />\n除左呢段日子要政權跪低<br />\n當佢唔跪低既時候<br />\n就只能推翻佢自己當家作主<br />\n<br />\n所以除抗爭外<br />\n我哋亦要開始接受革命手段係能夠解決呢一連串既運動"},{"pid":"877baee3cfbe3390ca51d1043f7fa9436b77dea0","tid":1317650,"uid":124859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T08:13:13.000Z","msg":"推"}]}